title: List of Sunrisers (women's cricket) cricketers
text:
This is an alphabetical list of <a href="cricket">cricket</a>ers who have played for <a href="Sunrisers%20%28women%27s%20cricket%29">Sunrisers</a> since their founding in 2020. They first played in the <a href="Rachael%20Heyhoe%20Flint%20Trophy">Rachael Heyhoe Flint Trophy</a>, a <a href="Limited%20overs%20cricket">50 over</a> competition that began in 2020. In 2021, the <a href="Women%27s%20Twenty20">Twenty20</a> <a href="Charlotte%20Edwards%20Cup">Charlotte Edwards Cup</a> was added to the women's domestic structure in England.
Players' names are followed by the years in which they were active as a Sunrisers player. Seasons given are first and last seasons; the player did not necessarily play in all the intervening seasons. Current players are shown as active to the latest season in which they played for the club. This list only includes players who appeared in at least one match for Sunrisers; players who were named in the team's squad for a season but did not play a match are not included.
